Hello <%= @user.email %> !<br/>
<br/>
Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.<br/>
<br/>
<% reset_password_link = "#{@front_url}/reset-password?reset_token=#{@token}" %>
<%= link_to reset_password_link do %>
   <button class="new-password-button">
     Choose a new password
   </button>
<% end %><br/>
<br/>
If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.<br/>
<br/>
Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.
